    <dt>Productivity.</dt>
    <dd>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://culturedcode.com/things/">Things</a>: the core task manager that runs my life.</li>
        <li><a href="https://bear.app">Bear</a>: all my knowledge, meeting notes, project overviews, etc. are stored here.</li>
        <li><a href="https://tot.rocks">Tot</a>: my scratchpad to quickly make small notes that sync. From here stuff goes to Things, Bear, or in a <span class="tag">void</span>.</li>
