        <li><a href="https://pasteapp.io">Paste</a>: a clipboard manager that makes it a lot easier to do a lot of copy+paste.</li>
      </ul>
    </dd>

    <dt>Code & design.</dt>
    <dd>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://zed.dev">Zed</a>: it is a nice fast editor, but I am not really tied to any particular editor.</li>
        <li><a href="https://ghostty.org">Ghostty</a>: a nice looking terminal.</li>
        <li><a href="https://vivaldi.com">Vivaldi</a>: every web developer needs a browser. This is mine.</li>
        <li><a href="https://www.figma.com">Figma</a>: I am no designer. But what I do, I do in Figma.</li>
        <li><a href="https://colorslurp.com">ColorSlurp</a>: my color picker of choice. Can't live without a color picker. Also contrast checker for WCAG 2.1.</li>
